node.text:
The most affected region by Coronavirus in Italy 💔 Lombardia is located in the center of Italy and Europe. Home to a variety of industries such as agriculture, manufacturing, fashion and eco-tourism. ⠀

The breathtaking landscape of Lombardy is a mixture of hills, mountains, lakes and plains. Its Alpine area is very popular in winter by skiers. Nature lovers are greeted by beautiful shoreline along the great Lombard lakes: Lake Garda, Lake Como, Lake Maggiore and Lake Iseo. ⠀

Stay strong Italy! 💚🤍❤️ #ForzaItalia

Video by @idressitalian ⠀

Always #wondermore

Visit: https://wonderlustcollective.co

node.text:
⠀
“Choose someone for your life who has the power to make you feel like you're floating.” ❤️ 

Cintia Zanuni lifts her up her husband who can’t stand on his own so they can appreciate the magical view together. This story is the ray of sunshine we need in our lives, encouraging us to always embark on new adventures and discover the world with the ones we love the most. 

Thank you for inspiring us @cinthiazanuni & @hugoecinthia 

📍Brazil 🇧🇷

📍Villa del Balbianello, Como, Italy

node.text:
⠀
Crazy footage of a massive rockslide in India 😱

🎥 via DDNewsLive/Twitter

The recipe for a rockslide is pretty straight forward. You need high altitude rocks, add bucket loads of rain that serve to decrease the resistance of the surrounding soil to downward movement (erosion) and let gravity do the rest. 

In this part of the world, monsoon season starts in June and ends in September, and certain regions will see 75% of their annual rainfall in this condensed span of time. Landslides and floods occur frequently and past seasons have displaced 2.5 million people due to these occurences. 

Our thoughts and prayers are with those affected 🙏❤️

📍Sangal Valley, India 

Via @natureismetal

node.text:
⠀
Incredible Tenganan swing in Bali, Indonesia 🇮🇩 🤩

Tag someone who should see this! 

🎥 by @juni_newman 

Meayunan is a traditional swing game for the people of Tenganan Village. This ancient village in Bali is indeed very unique. The settlement pattern still maintains the settlement pattern that they inherited down and down. The village is also famous for gringsing, ikat woven cloth which is only produced in this village.

Meayunan is only played once a year as part of a traditional ceremony. Usually done after the traditional mat Mekaré-kare, or popularly called pandanus war.

Meayunan is played by eight young girls. They sit in the traditional swing. On the right and left of the swinging pole, two young men were in charge of rotating the swing that the eight girls were riding on.

The two young men must turn the swing three times to the south and continued again with three rounds to the north. That’s the swing game system. Each must be done at least three times.

📍Bali, Indonesia 

#wondermore

📍 Sand Hollow State Park, Utah

Sand Hollow State Park is a state park located in Utah, USA, featuring a 1,322-acre (535 ha) reservoir and an extensive off highway vehicle recreation area on Sand Mountain. The park is near the town of Hurricane.

The park was officially dedicated in April 2003 and surrounds the Sand Hollow Reservoir. Sand Hollow quickly became a popular site for camping, fishing, boating, and ATV riding on nearby sand dunes.
